  Koh kong2 to3-tng2--lai5 piaN3-sau3 hit-jit8, tak8-hang7 mih8 theh8 chhut lai5 phak8, peng2-peng2 hiah-e5 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 mih8, Siok-cheng khoaN3-choe3 bo5 lou7-eng7--e5 long2 ka7 i hiat-kak8. Ki5-tiong u7 hiah-e5 chhit-chap8-tang5 peh-chap8-thih, put-tong7 li2-khian e5 mih8, Le7-hoa5 liah8 choe3 chin po2-poe3, pau chit8-pau chit8-pau un5-un5-a2 siu ho2-se3, lian5 chit8-sian liu3-phi2 liu3-phi2 bin7 ku7-khi3 niau-niau e5 ang5-a2, oa2 chiaN5-chhioh toa7, sou2 chheng7 e5 saN ia7 ku7-ku7-khi3 lah, ia7 chin m7-kam siu ho2-se3, Siok-cheng long2 khoaN3 choe3 bo5 lou7-eng7 ka7 i hiat-kak8, u7 e5 ka7 i pang3 hoe2-sio. 
  Le7-hoa5 khi3 thak8 Iu3-ti7-hng5 to3--lai5, khoaN3 chit8-e7 toa7 m7-kam, chin7 sou3 e7 khi3 khioh to3-tng2--lai5, tek8-piat8 hit sian ang5-a2 e5 saN u7 hou7 hoe2 sio-tioh8, chhiu2-kut chit8-ki ia7 sio2-khoa2 sio-tioh8, Le7-hoa5 kin2-khi3 tui3 hoe2-tiong kiu3 i chhut, lau5 bak8-sai2 chin m7-kam. Le7-hoa5 sui-jian5 si7 6 hoe3, ki5-sit8 chiah u7 5 hoe3 chiok, ni5-boe2 ut-hoe3 e5 kiaN2, chin m7-kam, khioh lai5 pho7 tiam3 heng-cheng5, kin2 khioh ma-ma e5 pou3-liau5-a2 lai5 ka7 i pau-chhiu2, na2-chun2 hou7-su7 chit8-iuN7 e5 koan-sim hoan7-chia2, koh kiu5 ma-ma ka7 i choe3 sin-saN. Siok-cheng khi2-thau5 khoaN3 liau2 ia7 ho2-khi3, ia7 ho2-chhio3, chong2-si7 au7-lai5 chiu7 siuN7 eng-kai tioh8 the2-thiap se3-kiaN2 e5 sim, chun-tiong7 se3-kiaN2 e5 sou2-iu2-koan5, mih8 si7 i e5, bo5 kap i chham-siong5, bo5 tit se3-kiaN2 e5 liong7-kai2, sui5-pian7 chiong lang5 khoaN3 choe3 ke-hoe2 e5 mih8 ka7 lang5 hiat-kak8, si7 bu5-si7 lang5 e5 jin5-koan5 e5 chun-giam5, koh tek8-piat tui3 i e5 ho2 peng5-iu2 ¡§Bi2-le7¡¨ (hit-sian ang5-a2 e5 mia5), ka7 i liah8 khi3 hou7 hoe2-sio koh-khah m7-tioh8, koe3-khi3 Bi2-le7 kap i khun3, hou7 i pho7, hou7 i aiN7, choe3 i e5 lang5-kheh hou7 i chhiaN2, i bo5 ti7-teh, lan2 chiu7 chiong i sou2 khoaN3 choe3 ho2 peng5-iu2 e5, ka7 i hiat hou7 hoe2-sio, chin-chiaN3 siong-tioh8 se3-kiaN2 e5 iu2-ji5-kam2, bok8-koai3 Le7-hoa5 siong-sim. TaN tioh8 oan5-seng5 i e5 nng2-sim e5 heng5-ui5 chiah ho2, siat-su2 lan2 na7 nge7-nge7 ka7 i chhiuN2 hiat-kak8, kong2 m7-thiaN, soa3 ka7 i phah, kong2 i sam-pat, kau3 hiah toa7-han3 lah iau2 teh sng2 ang5-a2, an2-ni chit8-sut-a2 tou bo5 li7-ek hit-e5 gin2-na2 e5 cheng-sin5 kau3-iok8, koh tian-to3 hou7 i giau5-gi5 lau7-bu2 e5 au2-hoaiN5, bo5 cheng5, bo5 thiaN3-sim, i beh m7-goan7 li2, khoaN3-khin lau7-bo2 e5 sou2-choe3, beh it-seng ki3-tit li2 e5 ia2-ban5, m7-na7 bo5 poe5-iok8 i e5 chu5-sim, iu2-gi5, koh hou7 i phau7 bo5-han7 e5 siong-pi-kam2, kap m7-kam-goan7 lau7-bu2 bo5 cheng5-li2, ko-ap-tek chhiu2-toaN7 e5 khoan2-thai7. 
  Siok-cheng siuN7-lai5 siuN7-khi3 chiu7 kin2 koh chiong lan5-san-pou3 the3 ¡§Bi2-le7¡¨ choe3 sin-saN, ia7 tui3 Le7-hoa5 hoe7 sit-le2, ka7 i kong2, Ma-ma chit8-si5 siuN7 bo5 tioh8, be7 ki3-tit mng7 Le7-hoa5 iau2 u7 khiam3-eng7 Bi2-le7 a2-bo5.¡¨ Tek-khak m7-thang bu5-si7 se3-kiaN2 e5 chu7-chun-sim. 
