  5. ¡§Phah hou7 li2 si2¡¨ 
  U7 chit8 jit8 Le7-hoa5 tui3 iu3-ti7-hng5 to3--lai5, seng-khu hui-siong5 la5-sam5, goan5-in si7 ti7 iu3-ti7-hng5 kap lang5 sng2-chui2, iu3-ti7-hng5 u7 phun3-chui2-ti5, ti5 te2 u7 chhi7 kim-hi5, hit jit8 kap ki5-u5 e5 gin2-na2 ti7 po2-bo2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 si5 thau khi3 sng2-chui2, sio hou3, chin sim-sek, chiok hoaN-hi2, sou2-i2 seng-khu soa3 phah-tam5. Au7-lai5 koh khi3 soa-a2-tui sng2, sou2-i2 seng-khu ko7 kau3 ou kui2-kui2, to3--lai5 e5 si5 ma-ma khoaN3 chit8-e7 hui-siong5 siu7-khi3, ti7 choe3-saN e5 pou3-chhng5 teng2 u7 chhioh, sui5-pian7 giah8 khi2--lai5 lian5-lian5 bo5 keng2 sou2-chai7 ka7 i but8 chin-che7-e7, chin khi3, sim phok8-phok8-chheng2, chhiu2 phi7-phi7-chhoah kong2, ¡§But8 chit8-e7 thau2-khui3 leh, e7 hou7 li2 khi3--si2, ian7-thau5 ka7 li2 kong2 seng-khu tioh8 m7-thang bak kiaN-lang5, li2 chiah thiau-i3-kou3 bak kiaN-lang5, an2-ni kiam2 e7 khoaN3-tit, chit8 seng-khu be7 su na2 kui2, ia7 teh lau5-phiN7, khoaN3 tioh8 chin-chheh¡¨, m7-goan7 koh ka7 i liam3 chit8-e7 kong2, ¡§Be7 tit lin2 pe7 si2, lioh8-a2 chiu7 leng2-tioh8 lau5-phiN7, li2 ia7 kaN2 sng2-chui2.¡¨ Le7-hoa5 tit8-tit8 hau2, ia7 thiaN3, ia7 kiaN. Tu2 hit si5 Le7-hoa5 e5 lau7-su, po2-bo2 tui3 hia koe3, i ia7 si7 lan2 kau3-hoe7 e5 chi2-moai7, i u7 thak8 koe3 lan2 Sin5-hak8-iN7 e5 po2-bo2-kho, iu3-ti7-hng5 ia7 si7 lan2 kau3-hoe7 siat--e5. I tui3 hia koe3 thiaN Le7-hoa5 teh hau2, chiu7 oat lai5 ka7 i khoaN3, khoaN3 Siok-cheng chip-su7 khi3 phut-phut, chhiu2 iau2-ku2 giah8 chhioh, chiu7 oa2-khi3 eng7 chhio3-iong5 lai5 khou2-khng3 Siok-cheng chip-su7, soa3 hoe7 sit-le2 kong2, ¡§Chin sit-le2, in-ui7 goa2 sit chu3-i3 e5 kam-tok, sou2-i2 hou7 i khi3 bak-chui2, bak kau3 hiah tam5.¡¨ Siok-cheng chip-su7 ki3-jian5 khoaN3 po2-bo2 hiah chhio3-iong5, hiah chhin-chhiat teh hoe7, ka-ki7 ia7 chin phaiN2-se3, chhioh pang3 leh, chiu7 khan Le7-hoa5 lai5 oaN7-saN. 
